<task id="whr-custom-css-pt-oxy">
  <title>Publishing from Oxygen XML Editor/Author</title>
  <taskbody>
    <context>
      <note type="fastpath">
        <p>You can specify an additional CSS in a <term keyref="glossentry-wh-publishing-template"
          />. </p>
        <p>Open the associated <xref keyref="whr-template-descriptor">publishing template
            descriptor</xref> and specify the CSS in the <xref keyref="whr-template-resources"
              ><term>resources</term></xref> section. </p>
        <codeblock outputclass="language-xml">&lt;publishing-template>
    ...
    &lt;webhelp>
        ...                
        &lt;resources>            
            ...          
            &lt;css file="resources/wh_footer.css"/></codeblock>
      </note>          
        <p>As a practical example, the following procedure can be used to change the background
        color of the footer bar in the WebHelp output of the <b>Oxygen XML Editor</b> User
        Guide.</p></context>    
  </taskbody>
</task>
